            "body": "I don't think this is a bug. The same happens in Vim if you call `bufload('%')`:\n```vim\ncall bufload('%')\nif has('persistent_undo')\n  set undofile\n  set undodir=$HOME/.undo_dir\nendif\n```\nand it works fine if you set `'undofile'` after setting `'undodir'`:\n```vim\ncall bufload('%')\nif has('persistent_undo')\n  set undodir=$HOME/.undo_dir\n  set undofile\nendif\n```",
